sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente
    participant A as API
    participant O as Order Service
    participant P as Payment Gateway
    participant Q as Queue
    participant W as Worker
    participant E as Email Service

    C->>A: POST /orders
    A->>O: createOrder(userId, items)
    O->>O: validateItems(items)
    O->>O: calculateTotal()
    O->>P: processPayment(total)
    activate P
    P-->>O: payment_id
    deactivate P
    O->>Q: Publish order.created
    Q-->>O: published
    O-->>A: order
    A-->>C: 201 Created

    Note over W: Async Processing
    W->>Q: Consume order.created
    Q-->>W: order
    W->>W: reserveStock(items)
    W->>W: sendConfirmationEmail()
    W->>W: logOrder()
    W->>Q: Acknowledge
    Q-->>W: acknowledged

    C->>A: GET /orders/{id}
    A->>O: getOrder(id)
    O-->>A: order
    A-->>C: order